"```sql\nSELECT \n    ((SUM(CASE WHEN strftime('%Y', loan.date) = '1997' THEN loan.amount ELSE 0 END) - \n      SUM(CASE WHEN strftime('%Y', loan.date) = '1996' THEN loan.amount ELSE 0 END)) * 100.0 / \n     SUM(CASE WHEN strftime('%Y', loan.date) = '1996' THEN loan.amount ELSE 0 END)) AS growth_rate\nFROM \n    loan\nINNER JOIN \n    disp ON loan.account_id = disp.account_id\nINNER JOIN \n    client ON disp.client_id = client.client_id\nWHERE \n    client.gender = 'M'\nAND \n    (strftime('%Y', loan.date) = '1996' OR strftime('%Y', loan.date) = '1997');\n```"